parameters:
Hmm... Sometimes taking a walk at night is nice.
The air feels cool and refreshing.

I wonder if I should start running at night from
now on. Yeah, maybe I'll have some interesting
encounters then♪
??? Ah, it's such a pleasant night.
??? On a night as pleasant as this...
Don't you want to feel even better?!

Pervert: To think that simply exposing a body
separated by a mere piece of cloth could stir up
such intense emotions in people...

Pervert: Hmm...! I can't believe I forgot to take
off my panties...!

Pervert: Excuse me, madam. From now on, I will
shed my final shell and transform into a butterfly
that will flutter in this beautiful night.
Therefore, please do not miss the moment of my
rebirth...

??? Now! Today is the day you will surrender!
Capture them!

Pervert: Wha...!? S-Stop it, you guys! The
chrysalis before transformation is extremely
delicate...
??? Shut up! You perverted bastard! Be quiet!

Plainclothes Police Officer: We are the police who
were chasing after that man!

Plainclothes Police Officer: That person is a
pervert who repeatedly exposes themselves at the
perfect time on the night of the full moon, and we
have always just missed catching them.
....I must say, you're quite the pervert.

Plainclothes Police Officer: It seems this time
you were too distracted to notice us. Thank you
for your cooperation!

Plainclothes Police Officer: Well then, I'll take
my leave as well. Please be careful on your way
home at night.

Haah...! That was surprising... What an unexpected
encounter...

I wasn't looking for strange encounters like
that... Oh my...
Oh my... That pervert forgot their coat...

I guess I have no choice... I'll take it to the
police box...
Rei-san, what's wrong all of a sudden?
That coat... seems to be soaked in obscene energy.

That man, it seems he hasn't exposed himself
enough. It's as if his desires have imbued this
coat with obscene energy.

If an ordinary person unknowingly wears such a
cursed outfit, they will be influenced by its lewd
aura and become an exhibitionist.
Eh... So, should I... burn it?

Idiot! Don't say such foolish things! If you do
that, the lewd energy will only increase and it
will attach itself to someone else without
permission! It's a terrible idea, no matter how
you look at it.
Then, what should I do with this...?

...Fortunately, the original owner's sexual
preferences have been identified. Now, all that's
left is to satisfy the clothing.

I will expose myself in your place and release the
lewd energy!
(I knew it would turn out like this...)
I obtained a coat for exhibitionists.

There's no one around...! Should I try exposing
myself?

There's no one around...! Should I try exposing
myself?

I can hear voices in the distance...! Shall we try
exposing ourselves?
Huh...! A translucent body with a white kimono...
I-I can really see ghosts now...!

Ugh... But being able to see them is such a
strange sensation... This is an ability I could do
without...

No... I can't afford to cry... For Haru-kun's
sake... For Haru-kun's sake... Alright.

Ghost: I-I'm sorry... It's just that being seen by
someone for the first time got to me...

That's right! How dare this vulgar ghost!! Don't
you dare act all high and mighty in front of me!!
Do you want to be killed?! Hmph!!!
Hey! You can't intimidate like that!!

I'm sorry, this person is always like this. You
don't have to be scared.

So, is there a reason why the ghost can't find
peace...? Is there something they regret?

Yes, that's right. This person must have some
worries and is lingering in the mortal realm.
Ghost: ...!! Will you listen to my worries?!

When you interact like this, you seem like a
normal person. I might be getting a little less
scared.
Will you tell me about your worries?

Ghosts have started appearing in each map. Let's
try to find suspicious places.
Ghost: Will you listen to my story?
Ghost: U-um... I-I'm s-sorry... p-please listen...
Ghost: Let's go for a walk again, big sister!
Ghost: Big sister! Let's go for a walk!
Ghost: Let's go for a walk again, Pochi!

Ghost: Oh, Pochi! There's something I want to
confirm! Let's go for a walk.
Ghost: Yes... Please come back soon...
